Well, i know... it's a bit weird since i have told you guys on path and twitter. But, you know what? I just cant believe what I have done today and this thing just make me feel like I'm going back to the past. I suddenly remembered my first community service, back to 2010. At that time, i become one of the first volunteer from the weekly community service and served as the mentor.
In January 2014, I got the almost-the-same project in India and again, i become one of the volunteer who taught the indian kids at the NGO.

Semua ini seakan memberi saya gambaran, bahwa mungkin saja, di masa depan saya akan lebih banyak melakukan hal yang sama. Ini mungkin kebetulan, mungkin juga kesengajaan, tapi inilah yang membuat ini menjadi menarik.
